37
00:26:44,793 --> 00:26:54,593
公演中の撮影、録音、録画機材の使用は固くお断りいたします。
The use of photography, recording, and filming equipment during the performance is strictly prohibited.

38
00:26:57,593 --> 00:27:03,093
