The venue is completely non-smoking. Please refrain from smoking.

39
00:27:05,593 --> 00:27:12,593
万が一、具合が悪くなってしまった場合は、無理をせず近くのスタッフへお知らせください。
If you feel unwell, please do not push yourself and let a nearby staff member know.

40
00:27:15,793 --> 00:27:21,593
会場内でのモッシュ、ダイブ、大きく飛び跳ねる、
Acts within the venue such as mosh pits, diving, excessive jumping,

41
00:27:21,593 --> 00:27:31,393
ステージに物を投げ込むなど、他の皆様の迷惑になったり、公演を妨げる行為は一切禁止です。
throwing objects onto the stage, disturbing others, or obstructing the performance are strictly prohibited.

42
00:27:31,593 --> 00:27:34,593
ルールを守って盛り上がってください。
Please follow the rules and have a great time.

43
00:27:34,593 --> 00:27:41,393
みんな今日持ってきてくれてるうちわもね、高く掲げすぎないように気をつけてくださいね。
Everyone, please be careful not to hold up the fans you brought too high today.

44
00:27:42,793 --> 00:27:45,393
ありがとう。後ろの人見えなくなっちゃうからね。
Thank you. We don't want to block the view of the people behind you.

45
